{
  "stem": "9878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a man-- his name was Schlomo Berger, and he-- my father begged him he said smuggle me out, from there-- from-- because while the Germans [INAUDIBLE] people in the ghetto, they didn't count how many people are there, you know, because there, everybody was pushed into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then later on, if you are not registered, you don't get food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you don't get food, you die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's no place to get food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's all surrounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You can't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to go out with a special [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To go to work, you have to have something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they lived in a little room, I would say four by-- by eight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father built a little wooden-- wooden little benches on the [INAUDIBLE] where the kids used to sleep one, one, one on top of the other in order to be able to sleep through.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people who lived on the spot had already better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could get the best room of the-- of the apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But other people crowded in, and they crowded them in one area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they brought in people also from the outlying areas, not just from the--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they brought in people from outlying areas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As    a matter of fact, I-- from all the outlying villages, they brought down people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- of course the ghetto became overfilled more and more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they found it two ways.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Either people just starving to death, they just die out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they have control that they keep the people locked up in one-- one place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father, my brother, and some other people had a [INAUDIBLE], a working [INAUDIBLE] to go and work on the-- on the highway, going from Luck to Rocyzscze-- 19 kilometers that town, Rocyzscze.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
